Text:
Filerna är Ogg. 

4U WMA MP3 Converter är ett bra program för att konvertera till andra ljudformat :smile:

.ogg, is better than mp3 or wma, the best quality and the best sound ;)

you can use dbpower AMP converter, to convert .ogg into MP3

and, the ogg format, is less heavy than the mp3, great for the uploaders :D

Why would you want to convert from one lossy file format to another and thus lose quality twice? :unsure: Makes no sense to lower the quality, when there are players that can handle OGG as well as MP3.
These are all 96 kbps - most people will probably erase them right after discovering the bitrate. I did. That said, the quality is not bad for files encoded at 96 kbps.
